# data/ runtime layout (4open release):
#
# - data/sample/        small offline mirror, tracked in git for reviewer browsing
# - data/benchmark/     fetched by data/fetch_benchmark.py from Hugging Face
# - data/extracted_atoms/ and data/method_outputs/  fetched alongside the benchmark
#
# All three fetched directories are intentionally NOT tracked in git
# to keep the source repository code-only.  Anchor the patterns at the
# data/ root so the tracked offline mirror under data/sample/ is not ignored.
/benchmark/
/extracted_atoms/
/method_outputs/
!/sample/
